OceanView Roleplay

Welcome to OceanView Roleplay™

OceanView Roleplay (formerly known as SADOJRP™) is a dynamic and immersive roleplaying community dedicated to providing an engaging experience.

With a focus on realism, creativity, and collaboration, OceanView Roleplay offers a wide range of roles, from law enforcement and emergency services to civilians and businesses, all set within the vibrant world of San Andreas.

Our goal is to create a welcoming environment where players can build rich stories, develop their characters, and participate in a variety of roleplay scenarios.

Whether you're patrolling the streets as an officer, running a local business, or engaging in high-speed pursuits, OceanView Roleplay is committed to delivering high-quality roleplay experiences for everyone.

Join OceanView™ as we continue to grow and evolve, fostering a community where everyone’s contributions are valued, and the possibilities are endless.

What does OceanView have to offer?

Main Features

Built on Feedback

Got a suggestion? We'll listen. Suggest ideas within our official Discord® Forum, OceanView is built on community feedback, and we thank all of our players for their continued support!

Updates Landing Daily

OceanView offers tailormade experience updates on a daily basis to keep players occupied. These are designed specifically for OceanView to ensure that gameplay stays fresh and fun.

Community

Looking for a place you can call home? OceanView provides a peaceful and friendly environment, welcoming all players, all types of roleplay and friendly faces!

Active Moderation 24/7

At OceanView Roleplay, our dedicated team of moderators is here to ensure a safe and enjoyable environment for everyone—day or night. We’re always ready to address concerns, enforce rules, and keep the community running smoothly.

Purchase Properties

In OceanView Roleplay, you have the opportunity to purchase and own properties across San Andreas. Whether you're looking to invest in a cozy home, open a business, or secure a prime piece of real estate, our property system lets you build and expand your empire.

Active Roleplays

At OceanView Roleplay, the action never stops!
With our active community and dedicated players, you can dive into immersive roleplay scenarios anytime of the day.

OceanView City Roles

At OceanView Roleplay, the possibilities are endless! Whether you want to serve as a law enforcement officer, firefighter, EMS, or run your own business, there’s a role for everyone. xplore life as a civilian, take on thrilling jobs, or dive into the criminal underworld—the choice is yours. With a variety of roles to choose from, you can create your perfect character and shape your story in the world of San Andreas.

Dealership Functionality

In OceanView Roleplay, you have the power to grow your wealth and spend it how you choose—especially on vehicles! Using our custom economy system, you can work your way up and purchase cars, bikes, and more from dealerships across San Andreas.

Unique Scenes

At OceanView Roleplay, no two scenes are the same! With endless possibilities and dynamic roleplay, you can craft unique and memorable experiences every time you log in. Whether it’s a high-speed chase, an intense firefight, or a heartfelt civilian interaction, the OceanView community thrives on creativity.

Upcoming Drug System

OceanView Roleplay is about to take things to the next level with our upcoming drug system! Soon, you’ll be able to dive into the world of narcotics like never before—deal, trade, and manage drugs as part of a fully integrated, immersive roleplay experience.

Roleplay Quality Enhancement

Often overlooked, OceanView strives for realism with smaller improvements that enhance the quality of gameplay, one feature at a time. It's the kind of attention to detail that isn't always noticeable, but it feels better.

Official Enforcement Training

At OceanView Roleplay, we take law enforcement training seriously. Our professional enforcement trainers are here to guide you every step of the way, helping you achieve your goals of becoming an officer, deputy, corporal, or joining any police division.
